        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>（题目链接：https://codeforces.com/problemset/problem/1662/A）<br>
（我的提交：https://codeforces.com/contest/1662/submission/155829485）</p>
<h2 id="1-题意">1. 题意</h2>
<p>Gianni收到了<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">n</span></span></span></span>道题目，每道题目都有难度 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>d</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>≤</mo><msub><mi>d</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>≤</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">d_i (1 \le d_i \le 10)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault">d</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.31166399999999994em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≤</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.84444em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault">d</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.31166399999999994em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≤</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span> 和美丽值 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>b</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>≤</mo><msub><mi>b</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>≤</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">b_i (1 \le b_i \le 10)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault">b</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.31166399999999994em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≤</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.84444em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault">b</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.31166399999999994em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≤</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span> 。如果没有一道题对应着难度 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>d</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">d</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">d</span></span></span></span> ，Gianni将会继续找同事索要题目。否则，Gianni会在每一个难度中挑选美丽值最大的题，然后把挑选出来的题编成习题集。如果Gianni需要找同事索要题目，你需输出<code>MOREPROBLEMS</code>，否则输出习题集里所有的题的美丽值的总和。</p>
<h2 id="2-思路">2. 思路</h2>
<ul>
<li>维护一个数组，数组的下标为难度，数组的元素代表其对应的难度中所有题目的美丽值的最大值，随后把此数组所有元素初始化为<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>；</li>
<li>在输入时，计算出对于每个难度中所有题目的美丽值的最大值；</li>
<li>如果数组中有元素为<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>，说明那个元素所对应的难度中没有题目，输出<code>MOREPROBLEMS</code>；</li>
<li>否则，输出此数组所有元素的总和。</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="3-代码">3. 代码</h2>
<pre><code class="language-cpp">// SWERC 2021-2022 - Online Mirror (Unrated, ICPC Rules, Teams Preferred) - A. Organizing SWERC
#include &lt;cstring&gt;    // for memset()
#include &lt;iostream&gt;
#include &lt;numeric&gt;    // for accumulate()

#define OPTIMIZE() do {             \
    ios::sync_with_stdio(false);    \
    cin.tie(nullptr);               \
    cout.tie(nullptr);              \
} while (0);

using namespace std;

void solve() {
    int n;
    int problems[15];    // 存储习题集，长度为15是为了防止溢出

    cin &gt;&gt; n;
    memset(problems, 0, sizeof(problems));

    for (int i = 0; i &lt; n; i++) {
        int b, d;
        cin &gt;&gt; b &gt;&gt; d;

        problems[d] = max(problems[d], b);    // 更新难度d代表的所有题目的美丽值的最大值
    }
    
    // 判断是否需要索要题目
    if (n &lt; 10) {
        cout &lt;&lt; &quot;MOREPROBLEMS&quot; &lt;&lt; endl;
        return;
    }

    for (int i = 1; i &lt;= 10; i++) {
        if (problems[i] == 0) {
            cout &lt;&lt; &quot;MOREPROBLEMS&quot; &lt;&lt; endl;
            return;
        }
    }

    cout &lt;&lt; accumulate(problems + 1, problems + 11, 0) &lt;&lt; endl;    // 求出习题集中所有题的总和
}

int main() {
    OPTIMIZE();

    int T;
    cin &gt;&gt; T;

    while (T--) {
        solve();
    }
    
    return 0;
}
</code></pre>
